pageContext.claim: “In Maryland, the Democrat candidate for governor wants to give illegal aliens free college tuition, courtesy of the American taxpayer.”
pageContext.analysis: Maryland Democrat Ben Jealous has proposed to provide free community college tuition for all Maryland residents, including undocumented immigrants brought to the United States as children, commonly referred to as “dreamers.” Trump himself has claimed he would like to find a way for Dreamers to stay. Gov. Larry Hogan, a Republican, has said he believes “dreamers” ought to be able to qualify for tuition aid at community colleges.
